🛡️ The Blue Team Master Bible (Sentinel Edition)
A Multi-Volume Compendium for SOC, DFIR, and Security Leadership
!
This repository serves as a Living Encyclopedia of defensive security operations. It transitions from low-level packet analysis to high-level executive strategy (GRC). Each volume contains theoretical depth, practical "Master Code" scripts, and verified industry resources.
🗺️ Master Curriculum & Volume Deep-Dive
📡 Phase 1: The Foundation (Infrastructure)
• Volume 01: Networking Battlefield
• Focus: OSI Layer 1-7, TCP/IP Steganography, Packet Crafting.
• Resources: TCP/IP Illustrated PDF | Wireshark Official Docs
• Volume 02: SOC Operations
• Focus: SIEM Architecture (ELK/Splunk), Log Correlation, Alert Tuning.
• Resources: The Elastic Stack Guide | Sigma Rules Repository
• Volume 03: Linux Hardening
• Focus: Kernel Security, SELinux, Syscall Auditing.
• Resources: CIS Linux Benchmarks | Linux Audit Framework
🏰 Phase 2: Corporate Defense (Active Directory & Cloud)
• Volume 04: Windows Internals
• Focus: Kerberos Attacks (Golden/Silver Tickets), BloodHound, GPO Hardening.
• Resources: ADSecurity.org | SpecterOps Blog
• Volume 05: Cloud Security
• Focus: IAM Policy Least Privilege, S3/Blob Storage Security, CloudTrail.
• Resources: AWS Security Pillar PDF | Azure Security Benchmark
• Volume 07: Perimeter Defense
• Focus: Zero Trust, WireGuard VPN, pfSense, IDS/IPS (Snort/Suricata).
• Resources: NIST Guide to Firewalls
🔬 Phase 3: Advanced Analysis (Malware & Forensics)
• Volume 08: Malware Analysis
• Focus: Static/Dynamic Analysis, Ghidra, x64dbg, Unpacking Ransomware.
• Resources: Practical Malware Analysis Labs | Any.Run Sandbox
• Volume 10: Digital Forensics (DFIR)
• Focus: RAM Acquisition (Volatility 3), Disk Imaging, Timeline Analysis (Plaso).
• Resources: SANS DFIR Cheat Sheets | The Sleuth Kit (TSK)
👔 Phase 4: Governance & Strategy (GRC)
• Volume 11: The CISO's Playbook
• Focus: Risk Management (ALE/SLE), NIST CSF 2.0, BCDR, Incident Response Policy.
• Resources: NIST CSF 2.0 Official PDF | ISO/IEC 27001 Requirements
🛠️ Sentinel Automated Tools
Each chapter includes a custom script to automate defense.
